MTN is running its #WeGotU promotion that allows users to double their data and voice bundles at no additional cost. To do this, customers need to do the following: Dial *142#
Press 1 for “double voice” or 2 for “double data”
Select the daily, weekly, or monthly bundle of their choice This offer is an extension the *142# service, which when called offers custom, discounted offers to MTN customers. “We want to show that #WeGotU is not just a campaign, it is how we at MTN think about our customers, making sure we are doing all we can to best meet their expectations and keep them connected,” said Mapula Bodibe, executive for MTN SA’s consumer business division. The #WeGotU promotion will run until the end of March. Read: MTN sees massive boost in full year earnings